description:
Explore the profound significance of the Sabbath as detailed in the Bible. It challenges the notion that the Church holds the authority to alter God's commandments, specifically the observance of the Sabbath. Look at the Bible to discover the unaltered truth about the Sabbath and its intended eternal observance in this thought-provoking exploration of Biblical teachings.
